{"tid":1162583,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"最喜愛的日本女主播2018出爐 她都進入殿堂級啦","createTime":"2019-05-20T03:11:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T03:11:53.000Z","uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"83ca6e99519e9ab889d3e3f6da53d76a89b76218","tid":1162583,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T03:11:53.000Z","msg":"ORICON NEWS網站按照年末慣例發行了&ldquo;最愛女主播排行榜&rdquo;，今年已經是第15屆。<br />\n<br />\n 值得一提的是，去年女主播水卜麻美已經連續五年奪冠，進入殿堂級，因此今年不參加排名啦~<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/translate/28/w640h188/20181207/h06G-hprknvt6469479.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Ftranslate%2F28%2Fw640h188%2F20181207%2Fh06G-hprknvt6469479.jpg&h=272cf733&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/translate/61/w640h221/20181207/NaLn-hprknvt6469495.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Ftranslate%2F61%2Fw640h221%2F20181207%2FNaLn-hprknvt6469495.jpg&h=cabd978b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/translate/39/w640h199/20181207/wRSa-hprknvt6469514.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Ftranslate%2F39%2Fw640h199%2F20181207%2FwRSa-hprknvt6469514.jpg&h=58e2f592&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/translate/33/w640h193/20181207/SyZT-hprknvt6469530.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Ftranslate%2F33%2Fw640h193%2F20181207%2FSyZT-hprknvt6469530.jpg&h=844d648e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/translate/55/w660h195/20181207/6neu-hprknvt6469552.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Ftranslate%2F55%2Fw660h195%2F20181207%2F6neu-hprknvt6469552.jpg&h=04ee59cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n真的是超級穩定的成績了！恭喜水卜麻美！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/translate/705/w448h257/20181207/a9Lj-hprknvt6469572.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Ftranslate%2F705%2Fw448h257%2F20181207%2Fa9Lj-hprknvt6469572.jpg&h=b0f8ae2f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n讓我們一起來看一下今年的榜單中有哪些大家熟悉的女主播呢？<br />\n<br />\n  第1名：有動由美子<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/translate/339/w512h627/20181207/I555-hprknvt6469581.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Ftranslate%2F339%2Fw512h627%2F20181207%2FI555-hprknvt6469581.jpg&h=95b457a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在今年榜單中，離開NHK電視台做自由女主播的有動由美子首次在該榜單中奪冠。<br />\n<br />\n  今年三月，有動由美子離開NHK電視台，她在NHK主持《STUDIO PARK TALK SHOW》、《ASAICHI》等節目備受好評，離開NHK後她在日本台主持《news zero》節目，去年排名第二今年奪冠。有投票者稱：&ldquo;有動由美子表裡如一，很喜歡她。&rdquo;還有觀眾稱讚說：&ldquo;有動由美子對工作很認真，經驗豐富，不做作。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n  第2名：弘中綾香<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/translate/324/w478h646/20181207/DhxB-hprknvt6469595.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Ftranslate%2F324%2Fw478h646%2F20181207%2FDhxB-hprknvt6469595.jpg&h=131ff721&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二名是首次進入榜單前十的朝日台女主播弘中綾香，她2013年加入朝日台，主持《Music Station》節目五年，今年九月畢業，另外她還主持一些綜藝節目，直播中的應對能力博得好評。弘中綾香看起來純真可愛，但說話一針見血，有投票者稱：&ldquo;弘中綾香總是元氣十足，對她很有好感。&rdquo;還有投票者稱：&ldquo;綜藝、問答、音樂等弘中綾香主持很多類型的節目，很多不同年齡層的人都喜歡她。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n  第3名：加藤綾子<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/translate/461/w541h720/20181207/yZBb-hprknvt6469619.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Ftranslate%2F461%2Fw541h720%2F20181207%2FyZBb-hprknvt6469619.jpg&h=178b6515&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2010年、2011年的榜單冠軍，去年排名第四的加藤綾子今年成了季軍，除了主持節目她還出演NHK連續劇小說《一半，藍色》，日劇《黑色止血鉗》等，社交網站關注度也很高。有投票者稱：&ldquo;加藤綾子有知性美，人也美。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n  第4名：川田裕美<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/translate/490/w545h745/20181207/VpCN-hprknvt6469651.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Ftranslate%2F490%2Fw545h745%2F20181207%2FVpCN-hprknvt6469651.jpg&h=30e94c90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第5名：德島繪里香 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/translate/307/w463h644/20181207/R9x7-hprknvt6469673.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Ftranslate%2F307%2Fw463h644%2F20181207%2FR9x7-hprknvt6469673.jpg&h=5ffbd184&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 第6名：大江麻里子 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/translate/214/w414h600/20181207/-VBL-hprknvt6469702.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Ftranslate%2F214%2Fw414h600%2F20181207%2F-VBL-hprknvt6469702.jpg&h=a25da4fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第7名：大下容子<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/translate/64/w374h490/20181207/cz6W-hprknvt6469737.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Ftranslate%2F64%2Fw374h490%2F20181207%2Fcz6W-hprknvt6469737.jpg&h=67056924&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 第8名：井上亞沙惠 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/translate/167/w410h557/20181207/vkuk-hprknvt6469775.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Ftranslate%2F167%2Fw410h557%2F20181207%2Fvkuk-hprknvt6469775.jpg&h=7f49aae3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第9名：宇垣美里 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/translate/503/w568h735/20181207/B1bJ-hprknvt6469812.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Ftranslate%2F503%2Fw568h735%2F20181207%2FB1bJ-hprknvt6469812.jpg&h=69bd7aef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第10名：田中美奈實 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://n.sinaimg.cn/translate/86/w384h502/20181207/fYhY-hprknvt6469845.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Ftranslate%2F86%2Fw384h502%2F20181207%2FfYhY-hprknvt6469845.jpg&h=f60e956f&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}